{
  "stem": "3040.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't necessary for our relationship that we know that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, yeah, went back, and I-- I found myself through the woods to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I boarded the train, and I came back to Debica.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was nightfall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't have to describe to you my feelings, my-- my fears, on that train, because there were very often the Germans came and examined papers and all this.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were checking out on people riding these trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it went through without an incident, and I arrived at Debica on the evening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to-- to the ghetto, but there was no ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a small area, three houses, surrounded with barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Before that, there was no-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It-- it was, you know, there was no barbed wire before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then, all of a sudden, then I knew that this is-- must be the ghetto that was reduced.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were talking about reducing the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I found a hole in that-- in one of the-- in the-- in the barbed wire, and I went in to the first house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I told them who I am-- oh-- and I'm looking for my wife.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Oh, your wife is here in the-- the next house, and they took me there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when she saw me, she fainted, because she didn't imagine that I would escape, and I-- I would be here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She-- she-- she gave me up for dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were reunited for a very short time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at the-- we used that-- I couldn't show myself in the ghetto, make myself, my presence, known because I was not legal there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was not supposed to be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
